<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>QUẢN LÝ SẢN PHẨM</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f6f9;
    }

    /* Navbar */
    .navbar-custom {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff7e5f, #ff4b2b);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }

    .navbar-custom .nav-link {
      color: #fff !important;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .navbar-custom .nav-link:hover {
      color: #ffe066 !important;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .navbar-brand {
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      color: #fff !important;
    }

    .username-badge {
      background: #ffe066;
      color: #212529;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 3px 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* Hero section */
    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 50px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff4b2b, #ff7e5f);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }

    .hero p {
      color: #6c757d;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-custom">
    <div class="container">
      <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
        <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
      </button>
      <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
        <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
          <% if (currentUser) { %>
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/suppliers">Suppliers</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/products">Products</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link disabled">Hello,
                <span class="username-badge"><%= currentUser.username %></span>
              </a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/auth/logout">Logout</a></li>
          <% } else { %>
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/auth/login">Login</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/auth/register">Register</a></li>
          <% } %>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div class="container hero">
    <h1>Chào mừng đến với kho</h1>
    <p>Quản lý sản phẩm & nhà cung cấp một cách dễ dàng</p>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
